    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Need a car on a tight budget? Here's your chance to grab a set of wheels at a price that's hard to beat! We'll be straight with you \u2014 this car is in poor condition. It does start and move under its own power, but it has noticeable mechanical issues and visible wear and tear throughout. This is best suited for a handy buyer looking for a project, a parts car, or simply the most affordable way to get from point A to point B. If you're willing to put in some work or just need basic transportation, this could be the deal you've been waiting for!",
