      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd29 Budget Buy with Honest Bones! \u2014 Looking for a no-surprises deal? Here it is! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has significant wear, mechanical issues that will need attention, and is best suited for a skilled DIYer, parts salvager, or someone looking for a serious fixer-upper project. We're not going to dress it up as something it's not: this car needs work. But at this price point, it represents a real opportunity for the right buyer who knows their way around a garage. Come take a look and see if it fits your needs \u2014 priced to reflect exactly what it is!",
