      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with every potential buyer. The exterior shows significant wear throughout, including visible rust, multiple dents, scratches, and paint that is faded and peeling in several areas. The interior is similarly worn \u2014 expect torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration consistent with age and heavy use. Mechanically, this car requires attention and likely needs repairs before it can be considered fully reliable for daily driving. There may be issues with one or more systems, so a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly encouraged. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. Priced accordingly to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This is a truly exceptional vehicle in mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains its original deep luster, no scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel is straight, the trim is intact, and the glass is clear and chip-free. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor \u2014 pristine upholstery, spotless carpets, and all controls and features functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with confidence and smoothness. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, cooling \u2014 are in excellent working order. Service records are available and reflect consistent, proper care throughout the vehicle's life. This is a rare opportunity to own a used car that truly requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic touch-ups, no surprises. Buy with complete confidence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
